name: WindowInfo
description:
Information of the window to be
        shared.

parameters.windowId: The Window ID that identifies the window.

parameters.ownerName: The corresponding process of the window.

parameters.isOnScreen: Whether the window is shown on the screen.

parameters.width: The width of the window thumbnail (px).

parameters.height: The height of the window thumbnail (px).

parameters.originWidth: The original width of the window (px).

parameters.originHeight: The original height of the window (px).
